high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the microwave.
Take out the egg from the microwave, then close the microwave.
Put the egg in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Open the microwave and put the egg on the plate, to the left of the cup, then close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg on a plate in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the microwave.
Pick up the egg in the microwave.
Turn left to face the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Take the washed egg back to the microwave on the left.
Put the washed egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the microwave to the right of the range.
Open the microwave and remove the white egg from the middle of the blue plate and then close the microwave door.
Turn to the right and face the sink to the left of the coffee maker.
Place the egg in the sink to the right of the spatula, then rinse the egg with water to wash it, and then pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn to the left and face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the egg on the blue plate in the microwave to the left of the green glass, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg in the microwave.
